OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1784654322
OL,3,CMan, 74, sentenced for voyeurism after
OL,4,Cfilming schoolgirl on bus
OL,6,FA 74-year-old man has been sentenced
OL,7,Ffor voyeurism after videoing a
OL,8,Fschoolgirl on a public bus in Jersey.
OL,10,FDennis Sale was given 120 hours of
OL,11,Fcommunity service by the Magistrate's
OL,12,FCourt in St Helier, having filmed the
OL,13,F15-year-old girl on the top deck of
OL,14,Fthe number 15 service on 23 June last
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FHis behaviour was reported by a member
OL,18,Fof the public who the Magistrate
OL,19,Fpraised for speaking up, while
OL,20,Fdescribing Sale's actions as
OL,21,F"abhorrent".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
