PN,35802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1784654322
OL,3,CMan, 74, sentenced for voyeurism after
OL,4,Cfilming schoolgirl on bus
OL,6,FThe defendant sat opposite his victim,
OL,7,Fwho was dressed in her school uniform,
OL,8,Fand used his mobile phone to film the
OL,9,Fgirl's underwear.
OL,11,FShe was unaware of the recording,
OL,12,Fwhich was more than a minute long, but
OL,13,Fthe bystander called the police and
OL,14,FSale's phone was seized - where the
OL,15,Fvideo was found in his recently
OL,16,Fdeleted folder.
OL,18,FIn the UK, this would be classified as
OL,19,Fupskirting but it is not designated as
OL,20,Fa specific criminal offence in Jersey
OL,21,Fso falls under voyeurism.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1784654322
OL,3,CMan, 74, sentenced for voyeurism after
OL,4,Cfilming schoolgirl on bus
OL,6,FSale's Defence Advocate said he
OL,7,Frecognised what he had done was
OL,8,F"morally wrong" and he had deleted the
OL,9,Fvideo minutes after it had been taken.
OL,11,FThe Advocate added that Sale had "deep
OL,12,Fshame and disgust for himself" and he
OL,13,Ffully accepts he filmed the schoolgirl
OL,14,Ffor his own sexual gratification.
OL,16,FOfficers also found that Sale had
OL,17,Fsearched for pornography more than 600
OL,18,Ftimes later that day.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
