OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1784654322
OL,3,CMan, 74, sentenced for voyeurism after
OL,4,Cfilming schoolgirl on bus
OL,6,FThe Defence Advocate said his client
OL,7,Fhad become socially isolated and
OL,8,Flonely following his retirement,
OL,9,Fdeveloping an unhealthy pornographic
OL,10,Fuse, but that he was careful to ensure
OL,11,Fit was lawful.
OL,13,FIn sentencing, the Magistrate accepted
OL,14,Fthat Sale had not passed the video to
OL,15,Fanyone else and did not believe the
OL,16,Foffence was premediated, adding it was
OL,17,F"short-lived and out of character".
OL,19,FHowever, he stressed the vulnerability
OL,20,Fof the victim and that it was evident
OL,21,Fshe was a schoolgirl.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
