PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1784654322
OL,3,CMan, 74, sentenced for voyeurism after
OL,4,Cfilming schoolgirl on bus
OL,6,FAlongside his community service, Sale
OL,7,Fwill be placed on the sex offenders'
OL,8,Fregister.
OL,10,FAfterwards, he apologised to the
OL,11,Fcourt, saying he would never offend
OL,12,Fagain.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/5
